    <item>
      <title>为什么人工智能如此昂贵</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-30/why-artificial-intelligence-is-so-expensive</link>
      <description><![CDATA[推动更大的人工智能模型以及更多的芯片和数据中心来支持构建它们，正在推高科技公司的成本。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-30/why-artificial-intelligence-is-so-expensive</guid>
